column1:
1. Candidates from the eligible list are normally appointed to vacancies in the lower pay grade positions.
2. Annual salary is at the start of the pay range.
3. The current salary range is subject to change.
4. Please confirm the starting salary with the hiring department before accepting a job offer.
5. For information regarding reciprocity between the City of Los Angeles departments and LADWP, go to http://per.lacity.org/Reciprocity_CityDepts_and_DWP.pdf.
